descriptionHTML:
Dynamic Watch Face is beautifully designed Watch Face that has swirl effect, go round and round all the along. See the orbital motion in blue color inside the watch and complimenting highlights that lit up the hours. Dynamic watch face features 24-Hour digital clock and 12-Hour analogue clock.
Watch360 focus is in creating professional looking watch faces. Each Watch Face is engineered by high quality design and took enormous time to choose the watch colors with soothing effect which ultimately makes the watch unmatchable and incomparable.
Key custom features:-

• Watch and mobile battery updates.
• Unread mails and text messages notification.
• Weather and humidity updates.
• Elegant and Orbit design.
• Faster recognition with icons.
• Ambient mode engineered with the latest wear Api makes your watch’s battery stronger than ever

This watch face is for rectangular and circular smart watches such as the LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G WATCH R, LG watch Urbane, Sony smartwatch 3, Asus Zenwatch and Samsung Gear Live. Visit our exclusive Watch face collection for Android Wear on our website www.frillroid.com.
